trates of CYP450 3A4, such as cyclosporine.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/159668/', '', 'Alprostadil, Indomethacin, Ibuprofen, Ubidecarenone, Adenosine, Regadenoson', 'Hemin, Conestat alfa, Betibeglogene autotemcel, Hyaluronidase, Streptokinase, Human C1-esterase inhibitor, Crizanlizumab, Lanadelumab, Icatibant', 1767369485);
